This is a map idea i have been thinking about for a while. It is a simple idea - tick tack toe, though to put a twist on it I wanted to create 3 different tick tack toe boards so that the X's and O's were in different locations. To hammer the idea home even more I changed the textures of each board. My idea stems off strategy for the player. Normal maps people play are always the same, people tend to use the same tactics to win. With this map I was hoping people would have to use three or more different tactics because of the differentiations of the layout and also the textures (glass is key in some of the boards).

The biggest problem I had while creating this map was getting the players into the individual boards at at the same time (without players going into all 3 boards). Good thing I have contact with {cDS} Worm - which is an awesome mapper / logic builder. He came up with the smarts to make SDK hammer do what i wanted! If interested in "Logic Spawning" (players randomly spawning in different areas of a map) {cDS} Worm created an awesome tutorial located here: http://cyberdeathsquad.com/forums/index.php?topic=8427.0

Big thanks to those that took the time for creating the textures that I am using for this map.

Enjoy ^^

This map is a re-upload of my original Dogz Arena 2 map.  I got tired of having to fix and edit the same file over and over and I'm sure it was confusing a lot of servers because i kept the same name which was fucking around with compatibility and so forth.

As such, I've tweaked it one last time.  all the textures are properly packed, all the problems have been solved.  Everything I can do has been done to make this the pristine, final edition of this map.  Sorry for all the confusion.

I urge those who've downloaded this map as the old version to remove and delete that file and add this version to their map list and servers.  Anyone who plays it will re-down load this do to the name change as steam will recognize it as a brand new map.

Thank you, guys, for all your tips, comment, and support in making this map as it was my first, and inspired me to continue making maps.  I hope to entertain you guys with fresh ideas in the future.

With that, I bring you the new, fully fuctional, completed, and (so I've been told "bad-ass-ier") version: gg_dogz_arena_ver2

Much love,

Bailey

This was the best way I found to achieve all achievements. Some complexive entities will make it easier to players to get those achievments as fast as they can. With this mappack, unlocking achievments will be cake, and you will get them way much faster than if you play other maps than these. ALMOST EVERY SINGLE ACHIEVEMENT!
Achievement_cooperation - main map - Multikill area - get a 4kill of any rifle in the 1HP lineup enemies area! - Bombsite area - plant and defuse bombs, this one will activate if both teams agree in pressing the two buttons at each spawn. - Hostages area - rescue more than 30 per round! - Normal play area - play normally like you would in a comun server, this can also be the place to try other stuff. - GODMODE area - call a friend and keep the firing button pressed, your friend won't die as long as you don't hit his head! (infinite ammo/health) - Cash area - need money? get it HERE! an automized system will set your cash to 16000 and back to 0, repeating this process until you reach the cash achievment. (uses mani admin and still not tested) - Props hole - Shoot the crates inside to get an achievement. Extra areas: - Healer - Buyzone
Achievement_bombing Eather join T if you want to plant the bomb, or CT if you want to defuse.
Achievement_easyround Add a CT bot automaticly win as many rounds as you want, just leave the server when you are finished.
Achievement_linedup Whats the best way to get weapon kills? THIS. Add CT bots and start the annihilation!
Achievement_massivekills Get those epic kill achievements, a simple grenade will trow the CT bots away!
Achievement_sknifed Sknifed - Kill a zoomed-in enemy sniper with a knife This is one of ten[+] achievements you can get in this level. Join T, add bots to CT and knife'em all!
Achievement_cash Get epic amounts of cash, doing absolutly nothing! (requires SourceMod installed, and it was not tested yet but I guess it should work)

This is an old achievement map I made long ago. It is very simple and I can say its the fastest map to get kills on. You join CT team and kill the bots who all spawn on the same spawn origin.

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WhnhkY8Fc3g

As you can see in the video I have a script which automatically respawns all the bots when they die, and sets their HP to 1 immediately, so you can kill them very fast, and also de-equips them everytime they respawn. The script also sets the bot_quota to 15 and sets mp_limitteams to 32, so you do not have to bother with the settings.

You need to host the server from Source Multiplayer Dedicated Server (install it from your Community Home -> Library -> Tools). Run it for the first time, then shut it down. Now go to your SteamApps\YOURACCOUNTNAME\source 2007 dedicated server\cstrike. This is your server files. Put the map in your maps folder.

Now install Sourcemod by following instructions here http://wiki.alliedmods.net/Installing_SourceMod
Put the plugins after you installed Sourcemod into SteamApps\YOURACCOUNTNAME\source 2007 dedicated server\cstrike\addons\sourcemod\plugins
Start your dedicated server and change the map to this map and have fun!
NOTE: There is limitation with this plugin. When you reach about 700 kills or about that, the server will crash. Just restart and rejoin it.

If you want a Weapon plugin so you can get Terrorist weapons, install this http://forums.alliedmods.net/showthread.php?p=1372828

Note: The unlimited ammo was not by me. Its made by rhelgeby and fixed by Kyle12 and Darkthrone.

If you like this map and plugin, thank me by joining FireWaLL Zombie: Reloaded at 206.212.243.130:27015 (populated 24/7) :)

Map for grenate & all weapons achievements
Enjoy!)

ABOUT

This map is designed to help players earn weapon kill achievements with ease; please refer to the ReadMe file for instructions on how to use it.

Start a game with 1 bot. Join CT or T to have their weapons. 
**Both sides have buy zones!**

To get 1000 kills in like 1 min - open console and write: mp_round_restart_delay 0
Also bots must have knifes only.

Map was made by BuDyA

To get ammo for the T weapons, press F2 when in a buy zone. It should restock your ammunition.

To get the most out of this map: 

Make sure console is enabled by going into options>controls>advanced and tick 'Enable developer console'

Load the map with 30 Terrorist bots

In the console (press ~ below escape) type mp_autoteambalance 0   press enter, then type  mp_limitteams 99   and press enter

You may want to disable weapons for the bots, untick all the bot's weapon choices before you create the match.

easyhostage_v2.bsp  goes into your cstrike/maps folder, usually C:\Program Files\Steam\Steamapps\Username\Counter-Strike Source\cstrike\maps

Don't reupload this file, is it even worth it? Yes it is worth it because its a legendary map and if you reupload ill bite your face off and eat all your babies.

Smell ya later,
Chris
